dren":["ttehukk8b2x961o8785vele"],"parent":"f3is89cwurzqcn2hq28ckqq","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"variational-graph-auto-encoders\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#variational-graph-auto-encoders\"></a>Variational Graph Auto Encoders</h1>\n<h2 id=\"metadata\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#metadata\"></a>Metadata</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Title: <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">Variational Graph Auto-Encoders (Private)</a></li>\n<li>Authors: <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">Thomas N. Kipf (Private)</a>, <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">Max Welling (Private)</a></li>\n<li>Date: <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">2016-11-21 (Private)</a></li>\n<li>Date Accessed: <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">2022-06-15 (Private)</a></li>\n<li>Date Added: <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">2022-06-15-23-11-01 (Private)</a></li>\n<li>Date Modified: <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">2022-11-26-18-57-01 (Private)</a></li>\n<li>URL: <a href=\"http://arxiv.org/abs/1611.07308\">http://arxiv.org/abs/1611.07308</a></li>\n<li>DOI: No DOI</li>\n<li>Citation Key: <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">kipfVariationalGraphAutoEncoders2016 (Private)</a></li>\n<li>Citations: 1627 citations (Semantic Scholar/arXiv) [2022-11-26]</li>\n<li>Publication Title: No publication title</li>\n<li>Journal Abbreviation: No publication title</li>\n<li>Item Type: <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">report (Private)</a></li>\n<li>PDF Attachments: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/9025336/mjvolk3/items/9025336/attachment/UIVEMQEC/reader\">Online PDF attachment</a></li>\n<li>Tags: <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">#Computer (Private)</a> Science - Machine Learning, <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">#Statistics (Private)</a> - Machine Learning, <a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">#🦌📚 (Private)</a></li>\n<li>Local Library: <a href=\"zotero://select/items/9025336\">Local Library</a></li>\n<li>Cloud Library: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/9025336/mjvolk3/library\">Cloud Library</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"abstract\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#abstract\"></a>Abstract</h2>\n<p>We introduce the variational graph auto-encoder (VGAE), a framework for unsupervised learning on graph-structured data based on the variational auto-encoder (VAE). This model makes use of latent variables and is capable of learning interpretable latent representations for undirected graphs. We demonstrate this model using a graph convolutional network (GCN) encoder and a simple inner product decoder. Our model achieves competitive results on a link prediction task in citation networks. In contrast to most existing models for unsupervised learning on graph-structured data and link prediction, our model can naturally incorporate node features, which significantly improves predictive performance on a number of benchmark datasets.</p>\n<h2 id=\"local-note\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#local-note\"></a>Local Note</h2>\n<p><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">Local Note (Private)</a></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/Parameter_Estimation/notes/ttehukk8b2x961o8785vele\">Annotations</a></li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"nuyfwd7iokzd7m9oax0cdx5","title":"Root","desc":"","updated":1662428184246,"created":1661538521294,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Zendron"},"contentHash":"9185b031f95deeced1275adbefc49c09","links":[],"anchors":{"parameter_estimation":{"type":"header","text":"Parameter_Estimation","value":"parameter_estimation","line":7,"column":0,"depth":2},"paper-export":{"type":"header","text":"Paper Export","value":"paper-export","line":9,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["m7o7r4jqe4jdwgsh3ia8sa4","2fib55e8qqux9scimc7a9gn","tz8wfy0bidyoi7cew6pxfi4","k0qo53e6jvew0mcyv49bu0e","xxezmgby3v2mlneka3t295g","9gt33emg7725ksj2t7f4p4v"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"## Parameter_Estimation\n\n## Paper Export\n- [paper.docx](./notes/export/paper.docx)\n- [paper.pdf](./notes/export/paper.pdf)"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableExportPodV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"alwaysPrompt"}},"insertNote":{"initialValue":"templates"},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"randomNote":{},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"vaults":[{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"Zendron"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":